│  ├─ expiryDate (TTL index)
│  └─ status (index)
│
├─ ratings_reviews
│  ├─ userId (index)
│  ├─ movieId (index)
│  ├─ rating (index)
│  ├─ compound index: {movieId, userId}
│  └─ TTL cleanup: 1 year
│
├─ watch_history
│  ├─ userId (index, shard key)
│  ├─ movieId (index)
│  ├─ watchedAt (index, TTL: 1 year)
│  └─ progress (last position)
│
├─ watchlists
│  ├─ userId (index, shard key)
│  ├─ movieIds (array, index)
│  └─ createdAt
│
└─ sessions
   ├─ userId (index)
   ├─ token (index)
   ├─ expiresAt (TTL index: auto-delete)
   └─ deviceInfo

REPLICATION & DURABILITY:
├─ Write concern: Majority (prevents data loss)
├─ Read preference: Secondary (load distribution)
├─ Backup frequency: Daily snapshots
├─ Cross-region backup: Enabled
├─ Recovery time objective (RTO): < 4 hours
└─ Recovery point objective (RPO): < 1 hour
```

