### **Job Lifecycle**
```
Service creates job
    │
    ▼
Job added to queue
    │
    ▼
Worker picks up job
    │
    ├─ On success → Complete & delete
    │
    └─ On failure (retries: 3)
        ├─ Retry 1 (1 min)
        ├─ Retry 2 (5 min)
        ├─ Retry 3 (30 min)
        └─ Failed → Dead Letter Queue (manual review)
```

