## Key Architecture Decisions

| Component | Choice | Reason |
|-----------|--------|--------|
| **Movies Storage** | CDN + S3 | Low latency, global distribution, cost efficient |
| **Cache** | Redis Cluster | High performance, scalability, pub/sub support |
| **Database** | MongoDB Sharded | Flexible schema, horizontal scaling, document model |
| **Message Queue** | RabbitMQ | Reliability, advanced routing, dead letter support |
| **Async Jobs** | BullMQ | Redis-backed, visual dashboard, retry logic |
| **API Framework** | Express.js | Node.js standard, mature, lightweight |
| **Deployment** | Kubernetes | Container orchestration, auto-scaling, HA |
| **Monitoring** | ELK + Prometheus | Open-source, comprehensive, cost-effective |

